\'s The Deuce. His talents landed him featured roles on bigger productions, receiving direction from legends such as Spike Lee, Steven Spielberg, and Martin Scorsese. After developing friendships with and learning from the filmmakers behind the projects, he grew inspired to make a different type of impact on the industry and wanted to get involved behind the camera. Zuzunaga assisted Latin American superstar Guillermo Ivan in producing Welcome to Acapulco, starring Michael Madsen and Paul Sorvino. Learning from the experience, he then decided to produce a movie he believed in and that led him to The Dirty Kind. He hasn\'t abandoned his first love of acting though, even making a cameo appearance in the movie as a low-brow pimp<br>\n         ',NULL,NULL,NULL,'4103344','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/images/nopicture/medium/name-2135195744._CB470041852_.png',1545847337),(124,'Tony Barber',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'7414588','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/images/nopicture/medium/name-2135195744._CB470041852_.png',1545847337),(125,'Amy Shoremount-Obra',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'8813645','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMDIyM2QwYjUtODU1OS00YWRjLWFkODQtYzI5M2E0MWI2MTk0XkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyNDc5ODI3MzI@._V1_UX214_CR0,0,214,317_AL_.jpg',1545843479),(126,'Shawn Shillingford',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'5226857','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/images/nopicture/medium/name-2135195744._CB470041852_.png',1545847337),(127,'Valentino Rudi',NULL,'Actor, Screenplay Writer, Martial Artist and Film Fighter.Writer, Originator, Producer, and Actor of \"Storm From The East\" (Narrative) (Pre-Production) Valentino is a martial arts practitioner, instructor, and film fighter with 30 years of experience. His martial arts training includes: various Korean, Japanese, and Chinese martial art styles with a concentration in Tai chi, Wushu, and self defense. He teaches and practices a northern Chinese style called Tong Bei which includes various forms such as Pi gua ( chopping fist) Fanzi Quan, Cha quan (long fist) and various Shaolin styles including tiger, snake, staff, fan, etc... his tai chi teaching includes both the yang and Chen styles with qi gong. Valentino is a certified instructor by one of China\'s greatest masters and kung fu film star, Zhao Changjun, shifu. The certification is through a lineage and chain of narration from one master to another. Valentino has won gold and bronze medals in competition. He is also a level testing judge and competition judge with recommendation by Grandmaster Wu Bing (Jet Li\'s coach). Valentino has appeared in several films including the Last Air Bender, as a film fighter and stuntman. Valentino has trained hundreds of students in the Zhao Changjun Wushu Institute and various colleges, schools, community centers, and summer programs. Valentino combines physical fitness, cross fitness, yoga, and sports as warm-ups in his class. He has experience in many physical movement disciplines and sports including soccer, boxing, and football.<br>\n         ',NULL,NULL,NULL,'3603140','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMDk5MzczNGMtNGI2YS00ZGNiLWE0NzYtMzc1NWRhZmI5NDI4XkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyMjQwMDg0Ng@@._V1_UY317_CR115,0,214,317_AL_.jpg',1545843479),(128,'Michelle Santiago',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'3491108','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/images/nopicture/medium/name-2135195744._CB470041852_.png',1545847337),(129,'James M Adams',NULL,'James Adams was born and raised in Philadelphia, PA. James is a writer (Power From Above), administrator, and actor, known for Creed (2015), The Upside (2018) and Glass (2019).<br><br>In Power From Above, \"God answers prayers\" is the simple yet powerful message of James Adams\'s autobiographical story about growing up in North Philadelphia and Mt. Airy. Power From Above is his story, told in Adams\'s likable, straightforward style. This inspirational story rests on one young man\'s simple, repeated, and trusting requests for God to take care of him. God, in turn, listens and answers. This book is stirring and uplifting. It is a lesson to every reader that there is no problem that cannot be overcome through steadfast faith.<br>\n         ',NULL,NULL,NULL,'7759754','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMjM1Mjk3MDY2MV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwOTY3NjYzNzE@._V1_UX214_CR0,0,214,317_AL_.jpg',1545843479),(130,'Shawn Gonzalez',NULL,'Shawn Gonzalez was born May 11,1986 in Philadelphia,Pennsylvania.The son of Sarah and Hector Gonzalez and is the youngest of 7 siblings.Shawn starting acting at a very young age always jumping in front of the home video camera entertaining his family and friends.Shawn even played a part in his school\'s play in 6th grade called (Little Joy Juniata Hood) at a Senior Citizen center entertaining the older crowd.As he got older he took acting serious and is now acting in Films and TV shows all over the east coast.<br>\n         ',NULL,NULL,NULL,'4285235','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/images/nopicture/medium/name-2135195744._CB470041852_.png',1545847337),(131,'Rigoberto Garcia',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'5630367','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMzQwZTNkMmItNzA1OS00NWU3LWIyMTMtYThmOTlhYWFmYjJmXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyNDI5NDY2NTY@._V1_UX214_CR0,0,214,317_AL_.jpg',1545843479),(132,'Michael William Kondyra',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'9424480','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BZjE4NmI4NzktOTM2Zi00OWIyLThiNjctNTE5YmFmN2Q4M2NiXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyMzcyMDIyOA@@._V1_UY317_CR23,0,214,317_AL_.jpg',1545843479),(133,'Matt Wier',NULL,'Matthew Wier was born in Bethpage, NY to Gene and Jerri-Lynn Wier in 1991. Wier is a graduate of Messiah College and obtained a B.S. in Molecular Biology. Wier currently resides in Philadelphia where he works as a biologist when not acting.<br><br>Wier\'s big break started in 2017 where he portrayed a party guest in the movie The Upside. Wier worked alongside Bryan Cranston, Kevin Hart, and Nicole Kidman in the film.<br><br>After a close-to-career-ending brush with the Weinstein scandal from The Upside, Wier\'s acting career was revived by Creed II in 2018. The beloved boxing movie franchise, which takes place from Wier\'s home city, was especially popular that year due to the recent Super Bowl victory of the Philadelphia Eagles. Wier starred alongside Sylvester Stallone, Dolph Lundgren, Tessa Thompson, and Michael B. Jordan.<br>\n         ','1991-04-09 00:00:00',NULL,'Bethpage, New York, USA','8857219','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/images/nopicture/medium/name-2135195744._CB470041852_.png',1545847337),(134,'Juan G. Sanchez',NULL,'Juan Gilberto Sanchez was born in Alice Tx on December 23 1974. Juan is known for his role as Alejandro Morales in 3 Days (2018). Raised by his mother Estela Trujillo a homemaker and step-father Raymundo Trujillo a mechanic in San Diego Tx. Juan grew up close to his grandfather Ernesto Sanchez a WWII veteran who groomed him for military service. Juan took an interest is sports such as: baseball, football, volleyball, track and cross-country throughout his school years. Juan attended Angelo State University In 1994, but dropped out of college to join the marines in 1995 where he deployed to the pacific. Juan moved to Lansdale PA in 2000 after completing military service in Kanoehe Bay Hawaii. Juan worked in many services industries, metal industries and pharmaceutical industries. In February 2013 Juan was diagnosed with cancer. After beating cancer, Juan married Leslie Arroyo-Sanchez in a private ceremony on July 12 2013. In November 2014, Juan got a protesters role in Act II \"The Audition\" starring Tyler Mane.<br>\n         ',NULL,NULL,NULL,'6970449','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/images/nopicture/medium/name-2135195744._CB470041852_.png',1545847337),(135,'Laura Jean','Laura Jean Rundle','Laura Jean is a North American actress, model, host, & motivational speaker. She is an award-winning actress and has been featured in a world-wide health campaign for Abbott Pharmaceu