ack. She is passionate about the Make-A-Wish Foundation, an organization that grants the wish of a child diagnosed with a life-threatening medical condition, and has raised thousands of dollars for the charity. Her love for Make-A-Wish began when she played the part of \'Vanessa Marks,\' a young girl battling cancer, in the movie \"November Christmas.\" Emily created a \'love box\' to keep on the set of \"November Christmas,\" which encouraged people to donate to the charity. Emily raised so much money that she decided that she would create a \'love box\' for every set she was on. From then on, her love and passion for the foundation only grew.<br>\n         ',NULL,NULL,NULL,'3014840','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BN2E5OGQzZTMtOTMyYS00MDQ1LWEyZTQtZmU3ODEwMzUyMDg1XkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyMTY0MDIyOQ@@._V1_UY317_CR104,0,214,317_AL_.jpg',1545843479),(292,'Nyasha Hatendi',NULL,NULL,'1981-09-14 00:00:00',NULL,'Washington, District of Columbia, USA','1812840','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMDI4NDE1YzYtYjc0Mi00MGVkLTllNmMtYmZmNDIxMjc0OWE5XkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyMjQwMDg0Ng@@._V1_UY317_CR51,0,214,317_AL_.jpg',1545843479),(293,'Amber Townsend',NULL,'Amber Townsend is a US-born, British/Syrian actress who grew up in Kuwait. She has had a passion for acting since she was 6 years old. She has been in countless musical productions and is breaking into the TV and film industry with determination and talent. She is a classically trained vocalist and flautist as well has having a unique knack for accents. She has traveled the world and aims to continue this through pursuing her acting career. Her hobbies include dancing, horse-riding, volleyball and hiking. She does what she loves.<br>\n         ',NULL,NULL,NULL,'6726867','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BYmVlMDhlN2ItNDRhOS00MjQxLWIxYTctOWFlOGUxNWE5NmQ0XkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyMjQwMDg0Ng@@._V1_UY317_CR16,0,214,317_AL_.jpg',1545843479),(294,'Aria Lyric Leabu',NULL,NULL,'2008-07-31 00:00:00',NULL,'Los Angeles, California, USA','650709