o classics such as Isabella in \'Measure for Measure\' and Yeliena in \'Uncle Vanya\' at the Workhouse Theatre. More recently she landed the starring role of Rosie in the first ever production of \'Porn Crackers\' which also starred Charley Speed (Britain\'s Top Model Judge), directed by well-known producer/director Ruth Boswell and written by Jan Woolf, awarded the Harold Pinter residency at the Hackney Empire, London. After playing a lead in the film \'Love on the High Side\' which won the audience vote at the Cannes 24 hour Film Festival, she booked the featured role of Ashlee Wilcox a tough drug addict on the top ITV1 series Bad Girls. Then appearing in the role of sexy Spanish con woman Dr Christina Lopez Rey in BBC1\'s popular daytime series Doctors.<br><br>A permanent and key member of the Pink Elephants theatre company which includes a very select group of professional actors worldwide.<br><br>Possessing a meticulous and passionate attitude towards her craft when preparing for roles and with an ever growing fan base worldwide, Sandra is definitely one to watch.<br><br>(2007) Completed US feature The Gift/Echelon Conspiracy as 2nd female lead playing Female Casino Technician alongside Edward Burns and Ving Rhames.<br><br>(2009) Rehearsing for two plays, developing a UK feature and busy with pre-production for upcoming UK Vampire feature.<br><br>(2011) Pre-production of US feature Femena directed by Matt Cimber with Sonia Braga and Paulie Rojas.<br>\n         ',NULL,NULL,NULL,'2289195','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMjYxOTE1OTctYWFiMi00ZWRmLWE0ZGItYzk0MjJkZTFmNWVhXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyMjQwMDg0Ng@@._V1_UY317_CR20,0,214,317_AL_.jpg',1545843479),(344,'Toni Anderson',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'3173932','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/images/nopicture/medium/name-2135195744._CB470041852_.png',1545850801),(345,'Ivan Bernal',NULL,'Ivan Bernal is an Actor & Producer from Mexico, raised in Dallas, Texas. With over 12 years of acting experience in the fields of Film , Theater (30+ Productions in Mexico, Dallas and L.A.) Television and Commercials recent credits include a guest star role in Telemundo\'s Soap Opera \"Bajo el Mismo Cielo\", Netflix: Real Rob, and starred as lead in the Cine Sony Mini Series \"La Vida es como el Cine\" airing now in 2018.<br><br>Ivan is a member of the Sag-Aftra Union for Actors. Being fully bilingual he has been able to work in both markets both Commercially and Theatrically. National Campaigns & Commercials. Most Recent: Direct Tv, 76 Gas Stations (2 spots) Target, Boost Mobile, McDonalds and Honda among others. His Dedication and perseverance has won him many achievements, He was invited by National Spanish Morning show \"Despierta America\" to show the struggle of a working actor in hollywood and to share his accomplishments on a two day segment followed by a Live Interview with the show hosts. Ivan is also the recipient of the Sinergia Award from the Frida Kahlo Theater in Los Angeles for Acting and in 2008 he was the winner of Best Actor in a Monologue for the Dallas Latino Theater Festival for the piece which he wrote and co-directed \"Mi Jefe\". Ivan is also a producer at Voxx Studios a Dubbing, Voice Over and Production House in Glendale CA. and casting producer for various Networks and Projects, including Telemundo\'s \"La Reina del Sur 2\", \"Milagros de Navidad\" and \"Mariposa de Barrio\" soap opera about Jenni Rivera. Ivan Bernal also worked as assistant producer in the Film \"Ofelia\" that won Best of Los Angeles in the 48 Hour Film Festival and went to France to compete at the Filmpalooza Film Festival. Ivan continues to grow as an Artist and Producer and hopes to one day own his own production company.<br><br>Follow My Journey: Instagram: instagram.com/el_ivanation/ youtube: youtube.com/channel/UC-l3huA0Kh5YpTO2WPq_RDw<br>\n         ',NULL,NULL,NULL,'3463361','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BNTIyMzlmMzItYmNhMC00MGVjLTkwMWYtOGQ3ZWIzZTVlYzkwXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyODQ0Nj