mation for <a href=\"https://nullrefer.com/?https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0126029?ref_=nmbio_mbio\">Shrek</a> (2001).<br><br>Abrams worked on the screenplay for <a href=\"https://nullrefer.com/?https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0120591?ref_=nmbio_mbio\">Armageddon</a> (1998) and co-created (as well as composing the opening theme of) <a href=\"https://nullrefer.com/?https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0134247?ref_=nmbio_mbio\">Felicity</a> (1998), which ran for four seasons. He founded the production company Bad Robot in 2001 with <a href=\"https://nullrefer.com/?https://www.imdb.com/name/nm1333357?ref_=nmbio_mbio\">Bryan Burk</a>. He created and executive-produced <a href=\"https://nullrefer.com/?https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0285333?ref_=nmbio_mbio\">Alias</a> (2001) and <a href=\"https://nullrefer.com/?https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0411008?ref_=nmbio_mbio\">Lost</a> (2004), composing the theme music for both, and co-writing episodes of \"Lost\". He also co-wrote and produced thriller <a href=\"https://nullrefer.com/?https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0206314?ref_=nmbio_mbio\">Joy Ride</a> (2001). He made his feature directing debut with <a href=\"https://nullrefer.com/?https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0317919?ref_=nmbio_mbio\">Mission: Impossible III</a> (2006), reinvigorating the series. He produced the hit mystery film <a href=\"https://nullrefer.com/?https://www.imdb.com/title/tt1060277?ref_=nmbio_mbio\">Cloverfield</a> (2008) and co-created <a href=\"https://nullrefer.com/?https://www.imdb.com/title/tt1119644?ref_=nmbio_mbio\">Fringe</a> (2008).<br><br>He directed the <a href=\"https://nullrefer.com/?https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0796366?ref_=nmbio_mbio\">Star Trek</a> (2009) reboot, proving successful with fans and newcomers to the franchise. He next directed <a href=\"https://nullrefer.com/?https://www.imdb.com/title/tt1650062?ref_=nmbio_mbio\">Super 8</a> (2011), co-produced by <a href=\"https://nullrefer.com/?https://www.imdb.com/name/nm0000229?ref_=nmbio_mbio\">Steven Spielberg</a> and produced <a href=\"https://nullrefer.com/?https://www.imdb.com/title/tt1229238?ref_=nmbio_mbio\">Mission: Impossible - Ghost Protocol</a> (2011). He returned to direct the follow-up to his reboot, <a href=\"https://nullrefer.com/?https://www.imdb.com/title/tt1408101?ref_=nmbio_mbio\">Star Trek: Into Darkness</a> (2013). Disney and Lucasfilm announced J.J. as their choice for director of the first episode in the new \'Star Wars\' trilogy, <a href=\"https://nullrefer.com/?https://www.imdb.com/title/tt2488496?ref_=nmbio_mbio\">Star Wars: The Force Awakens</a> (2015). He initially resisted, as he didn\'t want to travel away from his family to London, but <a href=\"https://nullrefer.com/?https://www.imdb.com/name/nm0005086?ref_=nmbio_mbio\">Kathleen Kennedy</a> convinced him that his voice would be the best to reinvigorate this franchise, as he had done with two others before. He also produced <a href=\"https://nullrefer.com/?https://www.imdb.com/title/tt2381249?ref_=nmbio_mbio\">Mission: Impossible - Rogue Nation</a> (2015) and <a href=\"https://nullrefer.com/?https://www.imdb.com/title/tt2660888?ref_=nmbio_mbio\">Star Trek: Beyond</a> (2016), and executive-produced <a href=\"https://nullrefer.com/?https://www.imdb.com/title/tt2527336?ref_=nmbio_mbio\">Star Wars: Episode VIII - The Last Jedi</a> (2017). When it was announced that <a href=\"https://nullrefer.com/?https://www.imdb.com/name/nm1119880?ref_=nmbio_mbio\">Colin Trevorrow</a> would no longer direct <a href=\"https://nullrefer.com/?https://www.imdb.com/title/tt2527338?ref_=nmbio_mbio\">Star Wars: Episode IX</a> (2019), it was announced that J.J. would return to complete the trilogy he started.<br>\n         ','1966-06-27 00:00:00',NULL,'New York City, New York, USA','0009190','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMTM4MTE0NTkzMV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwODEwNDU0OQ@@._V1_UX214_CR0,0,214,317_AL_.jpg',1545867002),(983,'Jo Burn',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'0122251','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/images/n