e-2135195744._CB470041852_.png',1545874201),(1291,'Reuben Johnson',NULL,'Reuben grew up in Salford, Manchester. Alongside his TV and Film career, Reuben is also an award winning stage actor and writer. He won the NSDF Best Emerging Artist Award for his play \'Territory\' at the 2009 Edinburgh Fringe Festival. Territory was subsequently developed into a feature film released in 2014.<br>\n         ',NULL,NULL,NULL,'4046100','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/images/nopicture/medium/name-2135195744._CB470041852_.png',1545874201),(1292,'Trevor Cooper',NULL,NULL,'1953-05-21 00:00:00',NULL,'London, England, UK','0178430','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMjQzNTM4NzkxM15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMjIyMTc3OTE@._V1_UY317_CR20,0,214,317_AL_.jpg',1545843479),(1293,'Kiera Bell',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'7659211','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BNDgwYjY1NDAtZTExOC00ZTc4LWIzYWYtZDQ0OWQ4ZjNkMTIxXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyMjQwMDg0Ng@@._V1_UY317_CR19,0,214,317_AL_.jpg',1545843479),(1294,'Christopher Marsh',NULL,'Christopher Michael Jo Marsh is an English Actor, born in Edgware, North London. He was educated at Ashmole Academy and went on to study at University of Hertfordshire, earning a BA (hons) degree in English Literature, Film, and Acting. Christopher later joined Chickenshed Theatre Company soon after graduating, where he trained in Inclusive Theatre.<br><br>Christopher is proud to be an official supporter of TigerTime, a campaign of the David Shepherd Wildlife Foundation on a mission to protect and save Tigers in the wild.<br>\n         ',NULL,NULL,NULL,'6764710','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/images/nopicture/medium/name-2135195744._CB470041852_.png',1545874201),(1295,'Bernardo Santos',NULL,'Bernardo Santos is an Actor who hails from London. He was originally born in Lisbon, Portugal. He speaks Portuguese, English and Spanish fluently.<br><br>Bernardo has been on various Feature Films and TV Series such as Tomb Raider, Hunter Killer and The Crown Season 2.