hen to circus team. In meantime he was performing as model and actor on many festivals and in numbers of commercials and festivals.<br><br>CEO of International Festivals in Poland and Incubator of Art, member of International Charity Organisations. Founder of House of Art in Lodz for artists and kids.<br><br>Nowadays he lives in UK and acting in movies , theatre plays, commercials and in spare time is teaching kids acting and circus craft.<br>\n         ','1983-06-17 00:00:00',NULL,'Poland','2630567','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BOThjOTc0ODMtYWRmNi00Mzg5LTk2N2ItODJjNjI1NTFmNmUwXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyNTUyNTAzMTU@._V1_UX214_CR0,0,214,317_AL_.jpg',1545843479),(1441,'Devlin Lloyd',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'6176818','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/images/nopicture/medium/name-2135195744._CB470041852_.png',1545877801),(1442,'Stephen McDade',NULL,'Stephen McDade was born in Guildford, Surrey and grew up in the small village of Bramley. He attended Bramley Primary School before completing his education at Glebelands School in Cranleigh. He has always had a strong love of films and theatre, and after years of working in other industries decided to move to working in front of the camera. He is married and has three children.<br>\n         ',NULL,NULL,NULL,'5387921','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/images/nopicture/medium/name-2135195744._CB470041852_.png',1545877801),(1443,'Robert McLanachan',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'8379671','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/images/nopicture/medium/name-2135195744._CB470041852_.png',1545877801),(1444,'James Merrill',NULL,'Ex semi professional boxer and ex armed forces turned actor after working at Warner Brothers as Jason Mamoa\'s body double/stand in on Justice League. Since then have been in many projects and always looking for new characters and roles. Recently made my theatre debut in Naked With Burger or Man by play write Sarah Stefanies.<br>\n         ',NULL,NULL,NULL,'9805497','https://m.media-