3479),(1464,'Daryl Smith-Wightman','Daryl Allen','Daryl was born in the ocean city of Plymouth, England. His parents were Kerry Allen and Bruce Smith-Wightman who later married when he was 13. He was the eldest of 4 children. His siblings were; Paris Smith-Wightman, Torr Smith-Wightman and Cheyenne Smith-Wightman in that order. He was quite a bright child but also a bit of a trouble maker. When he was seven years old he was diagnosed with ADHD. He would continue to get into fights and trouble with the police on a daily basis and soon his grades began to slip.<br><br>A few months after his seventeenth birthday he was kicked out of his home and from that moment on he began spiraling downward out of control. He spent the next few years in and out of housing organizations until he finally landed his first job as a carpet fitter, from that moment on he had the taste for money. He picked up several jobs to go along side his carpet fitting; bar tending, cleaning properties and for a short spell he was a naked butler. He maintained all this whilst going to gym almost everyday and playing football regularly. A few years passed and all seemed to be going well for this young lad who had so much potential and then he was laid off by his carpet firm. Stuck with no clue what to do, he decided to go back to college and get his GCSE\'s.<br><br>A year later and he had picked up the qualifications necessary to start a full time acting course. He passed this course with a Triple D*** and now spends his days, working at a coffee shop, going to the gym, playing football and chasing that one big opportunity that will cement his name in cinematic history.<br><br>Specialist skills; Globe Walking and Unicycling.<br>\n         ',NULL,NULL,NULL,'8521009','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/images/nopicture/medium/name-2135195744._CB470041852_.png',1545879275),(1465,'Clem So',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'6680316','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BNDE1ODcwNzQyM15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNz