images/M/MV5BMTQ5MzMwNjI4NF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwMTU5Mzc2Mw@@._V1_UY317_CR14,0,214,317_AL_.jpg',1545843479),(1507,'Javier Ronceros','Javier Reynaldo Ronceros Zender','Javier was born in Lima, Peru in a suburb called Mira Flores. He left Peru when he was age 3 and settled in Chicago, Illinois. When he was age 5, the folks decided to move to California were it would be warm in the winters. The family settled in Los Angeles. Javier\'s parents were both movie buffs and instilled the love of movies and Hollywood celebrities. Her desire was for Javier to grow up one day and be an actor. Javier attended no less than 7 primary schools before settling into Joseph Le Conte Junior High School in Hollywood, where he attended school there for 2 years. For secondary school, he moved to Fullerton, California and attended Fullerton Union High School where he excelled in tennis and was recruited to play at Cypress College. He had a long career in teaching tennis in South Carolina, Hawaii, Connecticut, and California. He ran a martial arts studio for a number of years. He began his acting career in Connecticut when he was approached by a filmmaker who asked him to be in his low budget action film. From that day forward, he feel in love with show business and has never looked back. He continues to act and is an accomplished writer, producer, and director. He has worked in the UK, Spain and the US.<br>\n         ','1959-10-07 00:00:00',NULL,'Peru','1242146','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BM2NiMzU2NzktZDg2Ni00ZTVjLWIzZjUtODU2NTg3NDliMDE2XkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyMjQwMDg0Ng@@._V1_UY317_CR131,0,214,317_AL_.jpg',1545843479),(1508,'Rosemary Dominguez',NULL,'Born in New York to a Dominican mother and an East Indian father, Rosemary Dominguez moved to Puerto Rico when she was 11 years old. She graduated from Columbia College in Chicago and went on to hone her theater skills performing with Chicago theater troupes such as Latino Chicago, Chameleon, Pegasus Players and an Arts in Education collaboration with the famed Goodman Theater. Most notably, Rose was one of the Lead actors in the premiere stage production of Sandra Cisneros\' The House on Mango Street, for which she received rave reviews from the Chicago Sun Times and the Chicago Tribune. Upon moving to New York, Rose was hired by legendary director Sidney Lumet for an episode of 100 CENTRE STREET. This was followed by roles on LAW&ORDER, THIRD WATCH and a comedy turn on Chris Rock\'s EVERYBODY HATES CHRIS. In Los Angeles, Rose found roles on GREY\'s ANATOMY, CRIMINAL MINDS, CSI, BODY OF PROOF, RINGER, a recurring role on REVENGE, the John Sayles\' Pilot, DR. DEL opposite Chloe Sevigny and a 4-episode Guest Star Arc on WISDOM OF THE CROWD opposite Monica Potter and Jeremy Piven. Recently Rose\'s career has turned towards the big screen. She was cast in not one but two feature films - PAPI CHULO with Matt Bomer and Paramount\'s INSTANT FAMILY opposite Mark Wahlberg, Rose Byrne and Octavia Spencer. Rosemary currently calls Los Angeles home where she lives with her husband and daughter.<br>\n         ',NULL,NULL,NULL,'1138507','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BNzU3MTU2MTQzMV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMzQ3OTI1MzE@._V1_UX214_CR0,0,214,317_AL_.jpg',1545843479),(1509,'Eve Harlow',NULL,NULL,'1989-06-20 00:00:00',NULL,'Moscow, RSFSR, USSR [now Russia]','2602672','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BYzUwMmIwNDYtZWE0MS00ZDI3LWJjNWItYmQ4ZWZlZjZhYWM4XkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyMjQwMDg0Ng@@._V1_UX214_CR0,0,214,317_AL_.jpg',1545843479),(1510,'Joselin Reyes',NULL,NULL,'1967-11-05 00:00:00',NULL,'Bronx, New York, USA','1242120','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/images/nopicture/medium/name-2135195744._CB470041852_.png',1545881401),(1511,'Connor Jones',NULL,'Connor Jones is an American actor, musician, and filmmaker from Atlanta, Georgia. Connor started performing and playing guitar at a young age and began acting at age 15, joining his theatre troupe in high school and falling in love with acting both on stage and on camera. At age 17, Connor started the band \'Neaptide\' with his 2 best friends, recording their debut EP at Southern Ground Studios in Nashville, Tennessee, home of The Foo Fighters\' \'Sonic Highways\' album, and releasing it in February of 2018 on all major streaming platforms. Along with his band and his acting, Connor works behind the camera as well, working on numerous indie film sets, as well as directing his own music video for his band.<br>\n         ',NULL,NULL,NULL,'8486968','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BZjE4ZDU0MzAtYzI1NC00NjJjLWJkMGYtYzFlYTcxZTAzNzBkXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyNjQ5NTAxNTU@._V1_UX214_CR0,0,214,317_AL_.jpg',1545843479),(1512,'Jaiden Byrd',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'4725662','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/images/nopicture/medium/name-2135195744._CB470041852_.png',1545881401),(1513,'James Arthur Sims',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'1022718',NULL,0),(1514,'Sarah Kirkpatrick',NULL,'Sarah Kirkpatrick is a happy and fun-loving little girl who got into acting after watching her older sister for many years in the field. Sarah enjoys acting and got her first big break playing \"Kimberly\" in the Mark Wahlberg film, Instant Family.<br><br>When Sarah is not acting she enjoys competitive cheerleading, horseback riding and playing with her bunny (Lucky Bam Bam) and her dog Wilma.<br>\n         ',NULL,NULL,NULL,'9653802','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BNmI0ZTZhYjAtMTI5Yy00ZmJiLThkZmEtZGEzMjlmZGNkNmE2XkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyODU4MTQ3Njg@._V1_UY317_CR19,0,214,317_AL_.jpg',1545843479),(1515,'John McConnell',NULL,'John McConnell has done lots of films and stuff. \"Spud\" was born in Gonzales, Louisiana.The typical middle child, he spent his youth trying to get somebody/anybody to notice him. When, after graduating high school, his dad wouldn\'t sign permission for his minor son to join the Air Force - instead insisting that he go to college - Spud chose Theatre as his major just to piss off the old man. He did a few plays, the girls noticed him, and the rest is history. Spud has worked on the East coast, the West Coast, but prefers living on the Gulf Coast. He lives in New Orleans where a bronze statue of his likeness stands on historic Canal Street.<br>\n         ','1958-11-13 00:00:00',NULL,'Baton Rouge, Louisiana, USA','0566279','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BZGRlNjhjZDgtOTNmNC00Nzc3LTlmMDAtNDcxMzA3NjhmODNjXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyNjY5NDc2MTg@._V1_UY317_CR159,0,214,317_AL_.jpg',1545843479),(1516,'Maureen Brennan',NULL,'Maureen Brennan was born and raised in New Orleans. She began her performing career at the age of 4 when she got lost at the shopping mall and wandered into a bar (yes, in New Orleans shopping malls have bars). While her mom was sought over the mall\'s public address system, little Maureen sat on top the bar, drinking Shirley Temples and singing for the amused \"patrons.\" She was a smash hit - and was hooked into a life upon the wicked stage (or in front of the screen, with any luck). After studying filmmaking at university, and a foray into standup comedy, Maureen settled into a comfortable life in Hollywood On The Bayou where she remains based today with husband, actor John McConnell and three kids.<br>\n         ','1959-06-15 00:00:00',NULL,NULL,'2163847','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BM2FjZDA4YWYtMTYzNi00ZGMyLWJkNTYtMzI5YzkzYzIwNjkyXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyNzgzMDAwODU@._V1_UY317_CR130,0,214,317_AL_.jpg',1545843479),(1517,'Kelly Tippens',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'1225114','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BNTUwNTg1OTEyNF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNTI0MDkxMDI@._V1_UY317_CR38,0,214,317_AL_.jpg',1545843479),(1518,'Charlie McDermott',NULL,NULL,'1990-04-06 00:00:00',NULL,'West Chester, Pennsylvania, USA','1668208','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMDc5MWI1OTMtODI2NC00YzEyLWI0MjgtMTljYjBhNDYyOGExXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyOTMzMDczMjE@._V1_UX214_CR0,0,214,317_AL_.jpg',1545843479),(1519,'Erika Bierman',NULL,'It is fitting that Erika was born in historic Savannah, Georgia which has been the site of several famous films. She expressed her desire to be an actress at the mere age of eight, when she begged her parents to let her compete in an acting/modeling competition in Orlando, Florida. She wrote her own monologue for the competition and got noticed by numerous reputable agents and managers.<br><br>Her first big break came when she was cast as President Snow\'s Granddaughter in the Hunger Games Catching Fire. She was thrilled to work alongside Donald Sutherland in both CATCHING FIRE and MOCKINGJAY I.<br><br>Later, she appeared in DUMB AND DUMBER TO, and worked with Jeff Daniels.<br><br>In August, 2015, she played \"Rose\" on the Peabody Award winning Sundance show Rectify.<br><br>Erika has voiced several commercials, including four for Little Caesars Hot-N-Ready Pizza commercials that aired on radio and television.<br><br>When Erika is not acting she enjoys gymnastics, dance, singing, writing and dressing up her teacup chihuahuas in various homemade costumes for our amusement.<br>\n         ',NULL,NULL,NULL,'4794787','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BYzVhMjg1NTEtYTU0MS00ZGYzLTk2ZTUtYTRiYjRmYzQ4OThlXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyMjU4MDgwMTU@._V1_UY317_CR130,0,214,317_AL_.jpg',1545843479),(1520,'Layla Felder',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'6463894','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BZDVjYjIwNmYtMTYyZS00YTkyLThjMDItY2I1MDllYmI0Y2Y0XkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyNTI0MjAyMzA@._V1_UY317_CR20,0,214,317_AL_.jpg',1545843479),(1521,'Candice Daniels',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'6930291','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/images/nopicture/medium/name-2135195744._CB470041852_.png',1545881401),(1522,'Carson Holmes',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'8324795','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BODFkMDhjZGEtNzZjZC00ZGM5LWI3OWItNWRhZGY1NjJjODUzXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyNjc0MTE1NTA@._V1_UY317_CR45,0,214,317_AL_.jpg',1545843479),(1523,'Nicholas Logan',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'3485972','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BYWQ3ZjAzMDAtM2NkNi00ZDI1LTg0M2YtZWQ2NjQwZDkyNTI5XkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyMTg2NzkxNTI@._V1_UX214_CR0,0,214,317_AL_.jpg',1545843479),(1524,'Allen Zwolle',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'1889772','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/images/nopicture/medium/name-2135195744._CB470041852_.png',1545881401),(1525,'Anthony Thomas',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'8463812','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/images/nopicture/medium/name-2135195744._CB470041852_.png',1545881401),(1526,'Stella Doyle',NULL,'She believes that ones passion is for a life time and it\'s better late than never that keeps her going. She grew up being instilled with strong work ethics working the agricultural fields of California. Surprising to learn she picked cotton, grapes, etc., and so much more for a living. Continuing her adventurous style she married a Seal Team One member, The elite group of the Navy. Well, if that was not enough, she added police officer to her resume, working out on patrol.<br><br>Her acting became apparent at an early age, putting on skits for mom and dad. She would round up the siblings to be \"extras\" in productions with her living room as her stage. Times were really tough for the family so delayed was the pursuit of acting. Decades later the opportunity came in the most unusual place; the Police Department; Filming industrial/training films. She continues to pursue her passion both in acting and as an animal advocate.<br>\n         ',NULL,NULL,NULL,'2348852','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BZDI1MDVlMDktYTA3OS00ZWVhLWE5OWEtM2YyNTZiOTM0Nzg2XkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyMTE5MzI2MjU@._V1_UY317_CR28,0,214,317_AL_.jpg',1545843479),(1527,'Andrene Ward-Hammond',NULL,'Andrene Ward-Hammond is a native of Brooklyn, New York. Growing up in a Jamaican household, she was exposed to a diverse element of culture and art. Her love for entertaining grew from observing the figures in her family and neighborhood, as well as, the films she digested growing up. Many of her influences were powerhouse performers like Whoopi Goldberg, Cicely Tyson, Don Cheadle and Meryl Streep. While in high school, Andrene cut her acting teeth studying improv at the local Jamaica Arts Center. She furthered her studies at Georgia State University in Atlanta, GA majoring in Communications with a concentration in PR and minoring in Psychology.<br><br>Upon moving to the South, Andrene brought her New York City hustle with her. She continued honing her skills as a member of the improv comedy troupe, Strange Groove and taking weekly acting classes at Premier Actors\' Network. It was here she met her longtime agent, Alexander White.<br><br>Andrene broke onto the acting scene as a character actress, making memorable appearances in television shows like, NCIS: New Orleans, Complications, and Being Mary Jane. With roles in FX\'s Atlanta and as caretaker Laura in period racial awards season romance, Loving, Ward-Hammond can be found on FOX\'s newest musical drama by Lee Daniels, Star and indie drama, Strange Weather with Holly Hunter and Carrie Coon.<br><br>The apple doesn\'t fall too far from the tree. Andrene\'s daughter, Tyla Harris is also a budding young actress making her mark in Hollywood. She plays \"Esther\" in the History Channel war drama, Six. Andrene, as well as her daughter are apart of the next breed of actresses leaving a lasting effect in Hollywood. With no signs of slowing down, Andrene exudes a fearless, dynamic energy her friends and supporters have coined by giving her the nickname Andreamin\'.<br>\n         ',NULL,NULL,NULL,'6292935','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BYzQ4MWI2ZTItZmVkYi00YTNlLThiZmYtOTdhNWY2ODE3OTMwXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyNTcwMzExMTc@._V1_UY317_CR131,0,214,317_AL_.jpg',1545843479),(1528,'Valente Rodriguez',NULL,NULL,'1961-02-14 00:00:00',NULL,'Edcouch, Texas, USA','0735538','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMDY2NjYzMTMtZDcyYy00MWQ2LTg0MDgtYzZmZWJmYThjZmNjXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyMTM5MjE4NjU@._V1_UX214_CR0,0,214,317_AL_.jpg',1545843479),(1529,'Denitra Isler',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'0411301','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMTYxMDA3O