ton Public, ER, Crossing Jordon, The Fugitive, Touched By An Angel, JAG and The Division among others. Television movies include Dead By Sunset on NBC and Gone In The Night for CBS.<br>\n         ',NULL,NULL,NULL,'0363669','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMjEzMjE4MTg3Nl5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNTkzNDQ1ODE@._V1_UX214_CR0,0,214,317_AL_.jpg',1545843479),(1597,'Brian King',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2444299','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BNmFlYzI3ZGQtNTI0NS00MDIzLTlhNjMtOGE1Nzc0MmZmYWJiXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyMTI5ODYyMzM@._V1_UX214_CR0,0,214,317_AL_.jpg',1545843479),(1598,'Ann Mitchell','Ann E. Mitchell',NULL,'1939-04-22 00:00:00',NULL,'Stepney, London, England, UK','0593129','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMTUzMDc2NTEzOF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTYwOTAyMDky._V1_UY317_CR85,0,214,317_AL_.jpg',1545846003),(1599,'Will Zahrn',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'0952040','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMTgwMTUyNzMwNV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwODkxMDEzOA@@._V1_UY317_CR6,0,214,317_AL_.jpg',1545846003),(1600,'Jacki Weaver','Jacqueline Ruth Weaver',NULL,'1947-05-25 00:00:00',NULL,'Sydney, New South Wales, Australia','0915865','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BNDYyOTg4NjkxN15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwMjA4NDU5OA@@._V1_UX214_CR0,0,214,317_AL_.jpg',1545846003),(1601,'Francis Florczyk',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'1010280',NULL,0),(1602,'Socorro Santiago',NULL,NULL,'1951-07-12 00:00:00',NULL,'New York City, New York, USA','0763640','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMTU2OTg4NzYzNl5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwNTg2MTkyMQ@@._V1_UY317_CR22,0,214,317_AL_.jpg',1545846003),(1603,'Stephen Hill',NULL,'Stephen Hill is an award winning actor (Best Male Actor, ABFF Star Project 2010), known for solid work in a variety of roles in film, TV, theater, web series, etc. Recently cast in the lead role of York in the HBO mini-series, Lewis & Clark, he is also on HBO, in Pete Chatmon\'s BlackCard, and in the fifth season of Boardwalk Empire in the recurring role of Clarence, right hand man to Jeffrey Wright\'s, Dr. Narciss