eside in the states. After her birth her family moved to Krakow and lived there until they migrated to the states. Early childhood she attended music school in Krakow with a focus on the classic piano.<br>\n         ',NULL,NULL,NULL,'8927267','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BNDA2ZDA3MzEtZDYwMy00ODA2LWFiMTItYTlkYmJkNDhhZGY4XkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyNTkxMDI2MjY@._V1_UX214_CR0,0,214,317_AL_.jpg',1545846003),(1669,'Thomas Hernandez',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'8916044','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMWM3MzI2MWYtOTkzZi00YjBkLTg4YmEtM2VkMzdmOTcyMmUwXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyMjQwMDg0Ng@@._V1_UY317_CR121,0,214,317_AL_.jpg',1545846003),(1670,'Connie Hollins',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'8309009',NULL,0),(1671,'Melanie Jewel Howard',NULL,'Melanie Jewel Howard is an actress, advocate, and artist. She received her J.D. from the University of North Carolina at Chapel Hill School of Law and works to empower youth. She is also a working multi-media artist. She resides in the Washington D.C. area and feels blessed to be on every set for television and film productions.<br>\n         ',NULL,NULL,NULL,'8036671','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BY2JkNWNlYzYtZjlhYS00ZTkxLWE4MTgtMDAyZDM5Mjk1OWRiXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyMjQwMDg0Ng@@._V1_UY317_CR32,0,214,317_AL_.jpg',1545846003),(1672,'Eric Ian',NULL,'Eric Ian Spent the first half of his life as a Skate-Boarder, when an unfortunate injury caused his career to end prematurely.. Ian quickly switched to print and runway modeling. After a few years he became bored with his career choice and embarked on an acting career that has been in the process of quickly developing into something beneficial and very exciting..<br>\n         ',NULL,NULL,NULL,'3130431','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BNTk3MDE2NTYxNV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwMTAxNjQ5MQ@@._V1_UX214_CR0,0,214,317_AL_.jpg',1545846003),(1673,'Brian Kayode-Patrick Johnson',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'7616196',NULL,0),(1674,'Steven Johnson',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'8328805',NULL,0),(1675,'Slim Khezri',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2278236',NULL,0),(1676,'Matthias Kocur',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'7758184',NULL,0),(1677,'John Krejczyk',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'8890144',NULL,0),(1678,'Tyler James Larkin',NULL,NULL,'1994-04-16 00:00:00',NULL,'Pittsburgh, Pennsylvania, USA','8275838','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BYjZmMDk2OTYtOTczZS00MmQxLThmZTQtZDYxZmYwOWU3MmEyXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyMjQwMDg0Ng@@._V1_UY317_CR9,0,214,317_AL_.jpg',1545846003),(1679,'Lizzy Leigh',NULL,'Lizzy Leigh was born Elizabeth Leigh Hinman to Rhea Elizabeth and Robert Lewis Hinman, Jr., where she came from a long line of modest folk artists and musicians. Her mother was a homemaker, who had talent singing, and her father, a business man with a passion for community theater.<br><br>Lizzy began her performing debut at age 3, where she fell in love with the stage dancing tap, ballet, jazz and drill, performing recitals, half time shows, parades and festivals. She started choreographing her own dance routines for performance and competition at the young age of 6.<br><br>By middle school, in her hometown of Cincinnati, Ohio, she was choreographing dance routines for her cheerleading squad which continued through high school and she became a charter member and captain of her high school dance team at Kings high school. Her senior year she auditioned and was selected to perform at the half time show of the Citrus Bowl. During this time, Lizzy was also taking hip hop from Carmen Electra and was the lead singer/dancer for an all girls teen singing and dancing group which recorded and performed around Cincinnati, choreographed by Shane Sparks of SYTYCD, Americas Best Dance Crew and You Got Served.<br><br>Lizzy fell head over heels in love with acting at the tender age of 6, performing in school, church and community theater. Not having taken any acting classes, she was an avid observer of the lives and reactions of everyday people from young childhood and would gather roles and character development by tapping in to those experiences. She ended up landing multiple lead roles in standard and musical plays, using those methods. She has always viewed her passion for performing as merely a way of life and how she was wired. From her perspective the performing arts all go hand in hand.<br><br>Lizzy sang from the time she was a baby and her love of music was only magnified performing onstage. She had numerous lead vocal roles in school, choir, public performances and recordings and was even selected for a lead in an Italian opera at her University (where she wasn\'t even a music major). Lizzy is niece to the late great Herb Belkin, a music industry innovator.<br><br>In college she pursued the behind the scenes technical aspects of video and audio production where she earned a B.S. in Broadcast Communications, from John Brown University. She felt this would help her gain knowledge dissecting every aspect of production performance. While in college she was additionally involved with assistant directing and landed a broadcast internship at the Summer Olympic Games.<br><br>Lizzy has worked professionally as an actress, singer, model, dancer, videographer, (a/v engineer/editor), scriptwriter for commercials, production coordinator, director and producer. She broke in to the industry just recently to audition for her first feature film after finding out some of her favorite and most respected modern day actresses were involved. She feels honored to work with and learn from the plethora of talent (both cast and crew) on her very first film.<br>\n         ','1975-02-26 00:00:00',NULL,'Lincoln, Nebraska, USA','6390610','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BOGYzYmYwODctYjdmYi00YjgzLWI1OTQtYjliYzFiZGI1OGFkXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyNTE5NDMxOTA@._V1_UX214_CR0,0,214,317_AL_.jpg',1545846003),(1680,'Erin Luboff',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2434356',NULL,0),(1681,'Nikia Lucas',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'9151821',NULL,0),(1682,'Phil Madura',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'8138293',NULL,0),(1683,'Barbara Elizabeth Maleski',NULL,'Barbara Elizabeth Maleski was born on April 10, 1964 in Highland Park, Illinois. She grew up in Deerfield, Illinois.<br><br>She was bitten by the acting bug, while living in Evanston, Illinois. She heard about an open casting call for The Express, which was shooting in Evanston. This was her first acting role, which led to many more in motion pictures & television.<br>\n         ',NULL,NULL,NULL,'3984343','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BZjgxNjcyYmMtZmMzZC00OGQ0LTkxMGUtNzg1M2U4ODY2YjlkXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyMjM0MzgzODQ@._V1_UY317_CR51,0,214,317_AL_.jpg',1545846003),(1684,'Shon McGregory',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'5682665','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BNDFjOTgyYjUtN2NlYy00YmFhLWIxNmUtZTFlNDM3MTQxYTM1XkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyNDI5NzAzODY@._V1_UY317_CR20,0,214,317_AL_.jpg',1545846003),(1685,'Annie McKinnie',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'8875390',NULL,0),(1686,'Freddy Moyano','Alfredo Moyano-Barroso','Born Alfredo Moyano, and based in the greater Chicago area, actor/voiceover artist, Freddy Moyano, owes his Freddy nickname to Wes Craven\'s Freddy Krueger, one of his favorite movie characters while growing up in Spain (1980s-1990s).<br><br>After having enough of working for private corporations (strong litigation/law enforcement background: 2002-2015) in the Midwest over the course of 14 years, Freddy founded his own production company and his active TV presence began in Los Angeles.<br><br>In 2016, Freddy co-hosted the motivational show \'Sergio Bruna Imparable!\' at the Los Angeles Convention Center. Bruna\'s infectious energy and passion as a mentor and reputable motivator, writer and TV host is what pushed Freddy to begin acting in and producing audiovisual content, taking over lead, supporting and background opportunities (Empire, Easy...) as well as a strong formation in advanced acting and stage combat.<br><br>Today, Freddy is known for his appearances in action films (such as Girl Assassin: The Search for Caesar (2018), Milkshake (2018), and soon to