st film acting role in Philadelphia by Heery Loftus Casting for Creed 2 on 05/03/2018. His role was Press/Reporter in scenes with Michael B Jordan, Wood Harris and Tessa Thompson. Eric Orr was born in East Orange, NJ and raised in a Christian household with loving parents who are now deceased. During his time in New Jersey Eric was an multi-sport athlete playing basketball and football he also performed in church plays and developed a love for acting but he needed a stable career so he attended Trade school to start a career as an Electrician landing a job at Pharmaceutical companies Schering- Plough and Merck he would then relocate to Hatfield, PA and continue his career as an Instrument Tech/ Electrician at Merck in Lansdale PA. Eric has a strong passion to help others in need and he is a friend to all<br>\n         ','1985-05-28 00:00:00',NULL,'Orange, New Jersey, USA','9883076','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BY2ZhOGM0MGQtMTIzMi00YWYxLTk2N2EtOWYyMWM0NWY4MzUyXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyODg4Mjk0Nzk@._V1_UY317_CR156,0,214,317_AL_.jpg',1545847150),(2053,'Lou Pacheco',NULL,NULL,'1964-10-25 00:00:00',NULL,'Cuba','3302647','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BOGZmY2JhOWQtYTBhMy00MWVlLWI2MjQtYzNmY2ZmOTA5NWQ1XkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyMTk4NDc4MzI@._V1_UY317_CR15,0,214,317_AL_.jpg',1545847150),(2054,'Robert Patriarca',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'4669367',NULL,0),(2055,'Sean Patrowich',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'5939205','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMjMwN2QxYjMtYjZkNy00NDIxLTkxMTYtNjNmZTU2OWExMTU0XkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyMjQwMDg0Ng@@._V1_UX214_CR0,0,214,317_AL_.jpg',1545847150),(2056,'Melissa Patton',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'5154359',NULL,0),(2057,'Stephen Perez',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'9204469','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMWNjYjI4MDQtYTI4Ny00NDkzLWI1MGItNGJhYTZjMzE5MDk1XkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyODEyMDEwODU@._V1_UY317_CR82,0,214,317_AL_.jpg',1545847150),(2058,'Roberta Pipito',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'1011505',NULL,0),(2059,'Ben Pobjoy',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'5842972',NULL,0),(2060,'Shelby Poston',NULL,'Shelby Poston is a Pennsylvanian native of Polish and Russian descent who likes to be called Shel. Along with acting, Shel is a director. She is the original director of a short play called \"Kearon and Kyle\" which first performed in 2018 at Watermelon One-Act Festival. She was the Assistant Director for \"Sherlock Holmes\" at her high school and directed \"Under Lubyanka Square\" her second year in college.<br><br>As a baby, Shel modeled for Boscov\'s and continued modeling again as she got older but her main focus is acting. Her acting career began in first grade where she was a part of a theater production. She has played soccer since age three, but stopped when she reached high school. She continued soccer once in college where she won the \"Second Team ALL-Region Women\'s Soccer Award for the National Junior College Athletic Association Region XIX\" in 2015. Concurrently, she worked at her college as the lighting designer for the springs 2016\'s production of \"A Lie of the Mind\" and in the spring of 2017 directed \"Under Lubyanka Square\".<br><br>In addition to soccer talents, Shel has experience playing basketball, track and field, dance, karate, and twirling. She had reached the level of brown belt in karate and participated in her school\'s Pac-10\'s for track and field for a few years. Shel has won a few twirling and dance awards and was even in Philadelphia\'s Thanksgiving Day Parade from 2007 through 2009 as a tap dancer.<br><br>Shel has also been a participant in choirs and in the spring of her junior year of high school traveled to London and Paris where she performed at Hampton Court and Notre Dame. After returning from Europe, Shel was an extra in the pilot of \"How to Get Away With Murder\". It is in that moment that Shel fell in love with film acting and decided to get more involved with the film world.<br><br>Shel did a pilot for Dream TV for Roku which sadly was never picked up.<br><br>Along with a love for acting, Shel also has a love for extreme sports.<br>\n         ',NULL,NULL,NULL,'7017219','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BYjc1OTRlZWYtMDBhMy00MmFiLTk1ZTMtNjM2YWYyNmMwODcyXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyNjAxNDI0MDc@._V1_UX214_CR0,0,214,317_AL_.jpg',1545847150),(2061,'Jennifer Bird Pownall',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'8408032','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BZTcxYTNmZWQtYWQwYy00YzM0LWE5ZTUtNDBhMDU2Y2ViNThhXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyNzA1OTkzMjY@._V1_UX214_CR0,0,214,317_AL_.jpg',1545847150),(2062,'Peter Presta',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'9295480',NULL,0),(2063,'Diezel Ramos',NULL,'Diezel Ramos Actor / Writer / Producer<br><br>Diezel Ramos, A 5 Time World Champion Powerlifter turned actor. Born in South Bronx NY on February 21 1977, to Italian and Puerto Rican/African American parents. Coming from a broken home and a troubled past, he managed to get himself out of the city and into Ocean City NJ where he met his daughters mom, Kim Richards and where life as he knew it would change for the best.<br><br>In 2010 Diezel\'s unique looks, size, and innate talent, was discovered by industry veterans. He was cast in his first principal role, in North Jersey, as a hit-man on Minikin. From that moment on his love for acting grew. With hard work, determination and a few challenges along the way, Ramos has landed many roles and voice-overs one would be proud of, such as,<br><br>White House Down Fast and The Furious The Last Which Hunter Transformers G.I Joe Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles Get Hard Olympus Has Fallen The Equalizer and Into The Storm<br><br>Not only did he manage to land great roles. He also became one of the few actors to portray characters for both<br><br>Marvel Studios & DC Entertainment<br><br>The Dark Knight Rises Man Of Steel Suicide Squad Batman v Superman: Dawn of Justice Kingsman: The Secret Service and 20th Century Fox production Fantastic Four<br><br>Ramos is definitely a talent on the rise and is a force to be reckoned with. He continues to thrive through his hard work and perseverance. It is no surprise that Hollywood is pounding on his rising star door!With upcoming productions in the next couple of months, Ramos will be keeping busy getting himself into character. One character being his first leading role, on the set of Garotte, is (Tiny) the mob bosses right hand man who\'s determined to find the truth, no matter the cost. Directed by Leo Sanderson. He\'ll also portray (Jose) on Messenger of Wrath Directed by Ryan Callaway (The Enforcer) on Streets of Philly and (Samson) on Vector III Retribution Directed by Micheal Farenilli. Thanks to Ellie B. Brown, he\'s also been added to her list of lead cast members for the Ellie B Block Party Show coming this fall of 2017.<br><br>Not only is he keeping busy with new roles and an upcoming show. He\'s also producing his first web production called \"Small Screen to Big Screen and Cooking in Between\". Which consists of reviewing & comparing featured films and Classic movies. All while preparing classic favorite foods and new foods with a twist.<br><br>Ramos isn\'t just passionate about acting, he also has a passion to help those in need. He has big plans to give back to his community by providing the homeless with care packages and meals. As well as help women, children and teens, that have been broken through different types of abuse, poverty and bullying. All by sharing his own personal story, to give them back hope and help them see the light at the end of the tunnel, the way he was once helped.<br><br>With his daughter Brianna Ramos as his #1 fan and his main inspiration, she gives him more of a reason to do great in this industry. He is determined to push forward and inspire as many people as he can through his work and personal character. One would say he\'s more than just an inspiration, some even say he\'s like a father or big brother, but he\'s definitely a friend to all. Those who know Diezel would say he is the most humble, hard working, persistent, wise, caring, straight forward kind of guy you\'d ever meet. He puts God first and goes above and beyond for those he loves and cares for which makes him a true Super Hero to many.<br><br>Check out Diezel Ramos on IMDB Facebook Instagram LUKE_CAGE_77 Writer / Producer<br>\n         ',NULL,NULL,NULL,'4516095','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BNGE0Y2E3ZTYtM2MzMy00NzNmLWJlMDktMzIxNzJjMjZjMGU0XkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyMjQwMDg0Ng@@._V1_UX214_CR0,0,214,317_AL_.jpg',1545847150),(2064,'Justin Robertson',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'6636884',NULL,0),(2065,'Krystal Rose Rodriguez',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'9525015','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BNWJmZWM0YzYtNDBjYS00NGI1LTkxZjQtMjliMDFhYmVmZGZmXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyNzAzMzQ4MzU@._V1_UY317_CR45,0,214,317_AL_.jpg',1545847150),(2066,'Chris Romrell',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'4684488','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMTc3Nzk3Njk2NV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNjQ3OTQ2NzE@._V1_UY317_CR15,0,214,317_AL_.jpg',1545847150),(2067,'Kerry Rose',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'7137213',NULL,0),(2068,'Danielle Ruch',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'8150608','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BZDBkM2E1YWUtYmI4OS00ZTllLWI5YTAtZmQ4NGI0ODc1MjZmXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyNjgxMjA3ODI@._V1_UY317_CR131,0,214,317_AL_.jpg',1545847150),(2069,'Neil Samuels',NULL,'Mr. Samuels graduated from Vassar College with distinction in Acting and Directing in 1980. He acted in New York City for several years - joining AFTRA when he was cast in As The World Turns (1956-2010) and, as a writer, he has had five screenplays optioned.<br><br>After a significant hiatus in the world of politics and marketing he has returned to his first love - acting. In 2013 he completed principal photography on <a href=\"https://nullrefer.com/?https://www.imdb.com/title/tt2525156?ref_=nmbio_mbio\">Kantemir</a> (2015), shot in Pittsburgh and starring <a href=\"https://nullrefer.com/?https://www.imdb.com/name/nm0000387?ref_=nmbio_mbio\">Robert Englund</a> and he then appeared on stage in New York at Playwrights Horizons as General William Tecumseh 